stories.title: Klusener helps bury Edgbaston ghost
stories.summary: It was the sort of batting revival which was more in keeping with the World Cup than the emotion-charged early evening at an over-flowing Wanderers but South Africa came back almost from the dead to bury the Edgbaston ghost
